These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
City: boston, marseilles
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, amber
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| City   | marseilles  | boston |
| Color       | fuchsia | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
House: victorian, palace
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the palace house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| House   | victorian | palace |
| Flower      | sunflower     | begonia  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
House: futuristic, gothic-revival
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| House   | futuristic | gothic-revival  |
| Transport   | roller | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different pets are kept: fish, ferret
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Pet   | ferret | fish   |
| Cigar       | ritmeester | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Birthday   | december    | august    |
| Transport   | car | tram |

 #################################

 
