.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, techno
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, horror
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | house  |
| Movie-Genre       | horror   | drama |

